---
import "../styles/custom.css"
const title = 'Pricing — Vectis Mail'
const description = 'Simple, transparent pricing. Start free, scale to enterprise.'
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
	<title>{title}</title>
	<meta name="description" content={description} />
	<meta property="og:title" content={title} />
	<meta property="og:description" content={description} />
	<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
	<meta property="og:url" content="https://vectismail.com/pricing" />
	<link rel="canonical" href="https://vectismail.com/pricing/" />
	<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
	<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
		"@context": "https://schema.org",
		"@type": "FAQPage",
		"mainEntity": [
			{
				"@type": "Question",
				"name": "Do I need a license to use Vectis Mail?",
				"acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The Starter tier is free forever with no license required. Pro is licensed through ValidonX." }
			},
			{
				"@type": "Question",
				"name": "What happens if my license expires?",
				"acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Your mail server keeps running. All core mail delivery continues. Pro features are gated but your data is never locked. There is a 30-day grace period." }
			},
			{
				"@type": "Question",
				"name": "Can I self-host without any external dependencies?",
				"acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. The Starter tier works fully offline. Pro checks ValidonX for entitlements, with a 30-day offline grace period." }
			},
			{
				"@type": "Question",
				"name": "What server do I need?",
				"acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Minimum: 2 vCPU, 4 GB RAM, 40 GB SSD, Ubuntu 22.04+. Recommended for production: 4 vCPU, 8 GB RAM, 100 GB SSD. Any VPS provider works." }
			}
		]
	})} />
</head>
<body class="marketing-page">
	<nav class="marketing-nav">
		<a href="/" class="logo"><img src="/logo.svg" alt="Vectis Mail" height="36" /></a>
		<div>
			<a href="/features">Features</a>
			<a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
			<a href="/getting-started">Docs</a>
			<a href="/about">About</a>
			<a href="/contact">Contact</a>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<section class="section" style="text-align: center;">
		<h2>Simple, transparent pricing</h2>
		<p class="subtitle">Start free. Upgrade when you need more.</p>

		<div class="pricing-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(280px, 380px)); justify-content: center;">
			<div class="pricing-card">
				<div class="tier">Starter</div>
				<div class="price">Free</div>
				<div class="period">forever</div>
				<ul>
					<li>Up to 3 domains</li>
					<li>Up to 25 mailboxes per domain</li>
					<li>Admin dashboard</li>
					<li>Webmail (Roundcube)</li>
					<li>Sending API + batch sending</li>
					<li>Inbound webhooks (full body)</li>
					<li>Sieve filter management</li>
					<li>DKIM/SPF/DMARC</li>
					<li>Automatic TLS</li>
					<li>Built-in monitoring (Prometheus + Grafana + Loki)</li>
					<li>IP warmup &amp; RBL monitoring</li>
					<li>Backup &amp; restore</li>
					<li>Community support</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="/getting-started/installation" class="btn-primary" style="display: block; text-align: center;">Get Started</a>
			</div>

			<div class="pricing-card featured">
				<div class="tier">Pro</div>
				<div class="price">$29</div>
				<div class="period">per tenant / month</div>
				<ul>
					<li>One subscription, unlimited Vectis installs</li>
					<li>Everything in Starter, plus:</li>
					<li>Unlimited domains</li>
					<li>Unlimited mailboxes per domain</li>
					<li>Per-domain analytics dashboard</li>
					<li>Per-domain spam controls &mdash; thresholds, greylisting, allow/block lists</li>
					<li>OIDC SSO</li>
					<li>Priority email support</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="https://validonx.com/checkout/vectis-pro" class="btn-primary" style="display: block; text-align: center;">Start Pro Trial</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<p class="subtitle" style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
			Need clustering, multi-tenant, or compliance features for a larger
			deployment? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> &mdash; we're shipping
			an Enterprise tier later in 2026.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
		<div class="feature-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));">
			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3>Do I need a license to use Vectis Mail?</h3>
				<p>The Starter tier is free forever with no license required. Pro is licensed through <a href="https://validonx.com" style="color: var(--sl-color-accent);">ValidonX</a>, our licensing and billing platform.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3>What happens if my Pro license expires?</h3>
				<p>Your mail server keeps running. All core mail delivery (Postfix, Dovecot) continues working. Pro features (analytics, advanced spam controls, OIDC SSO, unlimited domains and mailboxes) revert to Starter limits but your data is never locked. There is a 30-day grace period.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3>Can I self-host without any external dependencies?</h3>
				<p>Yes. The Starter tier works fully offline. Pro checks <a href="https://validonx.com" style="color: var(--sl-color-accent);">ValidonX</a> for entitlements, with a 30-day offline grace period and cached entitlements in Postgres.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3>What server do I need?</h3>
				<p>Minimum: 2 vCPU, 4 GB RAM, 40 GB SSD, Ubuntu 22.04+. Recommended for production: 4 vCPU, 8 GB RAM, 100 GB SSD. Any VPS provider works.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="footer">
		<span>&copy; 2026 Veltara Works. All rights reserved.</span>
		<div>
			<a href="/getting-started">Docs</a> &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
			<a href="https://github.com/Veltara-Works/vectis">GitHub</a> &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
			<a href="/contact">Contact</a>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>
